Navigation box displayed at the bottom of every [[Foundry Fridays]] DevBlog page, grouping entries by year. Uses the standard <code>{{Navbox}}</code> template with <code>autocollapse</code> state.

== Usage ==
Add <code><nowiki>{{Navbox Devblogs}}</nowiki></code> at the bottom of each DevBlog page:

<pre>
{{Navbox Devblogs}}
</pre>

This template takes no parameters — all DevBlog links are maintained directly inside the template itself.

== Maintaining the navigation list ==
To add a new DevBlog entry, edit [[Template:Navbox Devblogs]] and add a link to the appropriate year group in chronological order:

<pre>
| group2 = 2021
| list2  = [[DevBlog 42]] • [[DevBlog 43]] • [[DevBlog 44]]
</pre>

Year groups are numbered sequentially (<code>group1</code> = 2020, <code>group2</code> = 2021, <code>group3</code> = 2022). Add a new group when a new year begins.

== Notes ==
* The navbox uses <code>state=autocollapse</code>: it is collapsed when other navboxes are present on the same page, expanded when it is the only one.
* This template is sorted into [[:Category:Navigation templates]] and [[:Category:Templates]] via its own template page — not through this doc page.
